                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8403" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0391</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1719 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">权力的游戏——ZM公司组织政治的“七宗罪”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Game of Thrones - ZM&#39;s &quot;Seven Deadly SINS&quot; of Organizational Politics</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨茜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林外国语大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ZM公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织政治；引发组织政治的因素；不道德的组织政治策略；控制功能失调的组织政治；领导力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organizational politics, factors that cause organizational politics, unethical organizational politics strategies, dysfunctional organizational politics of control, leadership</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在很多知识密集型企业，其核心高管往往是创始团队中的重要成员，随着企业规模的扩大、专业人才的加入、组织能力的升级，一些能力不足的高管逐渐难以驾驭专业度越来越高的团队。对自身地位的不安全感、环境的不确定性、金字塔形组织结构、绩效的主观评价标准以及权谋倾向等很可能成为滋生组织政治的温床，当不道德的政治行为在组织中泛滥，极易引发组织政治的功能失调，伤害个人和组织，降低组织有效性。本案例以国内智能机器人行业黑马ZM公司的一系列组织政治事件为蓝本，勾勒了组织政治产生、发展、危害及修正等场景。使学习者了解组织政治，认识引发组织政治的因素，区分不道德的政治策略的类型，掌握对功能失调的组织政治进行控制的措施，提升学习者对组织行为的洞察和应对能力，树立权变管理意识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In many knowledge-intensive enterprises, the core executives are often important members of the founding team. With the expansion of the enterprise scale, the addition of professional talents, and the upgrading of organizational capabilities, some executives with insufficient ability gradually find it difficult to manage the team with increasing professional degree. The insecurity of one&#39;s own status, the uncertainty of the environment, the pyramidal organizational structure, the subjective evaluation criteria of performance and the machiever tendency are likely to become hotbeds for the breeding of organizational politics. When immoral political behaviors are rampant in organizations, it is easy to cause the dysfunction of organizational politics, harm individuals and organizations, and reduce the effectiveness of organizations. This case is based on a series of organizational political events of ZM company, a dark horse in the domestic intelligent robot industry, and Outlines the emergence, development, harm and correction of organizational politics. Enable learners to understand organizational politics, recognize the factors that cause organizational politics, distinguish the types of unethical political strategies, master the measures to control dysfunctional organizational politics, improve learners&#39; insight into organizational behavior and coping ability, and establish the awareness of contingency management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《领导力》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织政治的含义；引发组织政治的因素；不道德的组织政治策略的类型；控制功能失调的组织政治的措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
